channel.title: 317Random server crash, then a lot of "cannot resolve to a type & to a variable"
channel.description:
This is a 317 Project Insanity server from Acheron(or so it was named). I'm pretty sure nothing was wrong at first, because I started the server and it ran fine for a minute, but I clicked something in game I think and it crashed the server, when i started it, the cmd prompt was just rapidly closing and opening with an error.(in the pic)I went to where it said the problem was, and it looks fine to me, but I'm not an expert, so any help would be appreciated! There is an error out of no where when I compile too, but it doesn't make sense to me.
Server start error [img]http://i.imgur.com/1MtAKaE.jpg[/img] error location [img]http://i.imgur.com/Wb3f9wT.jpg[/img] Compile error [img]http://i.imgur.com/Xo8EIub.jpg[/img]

When you put this -> // before a line, it remove everything wroten on the line… This is the only reason that you get error while compiling and crash the server. Make sure to put the correct java variable on your computer setting too.

#Maximebasque (Main Creator of Acheron)
